  <Content>We are experiencing a high volume of downloads for Dark Ages 7.03, so the download will be slow. We recommend trying the mirror sites posted on the front page of www.planetda.net.

If you are having problems installing Dark Ages...

1) Delete your temporary internet files, you can do this in the Tools section of your browser.

2) Download the client again from the website, www.darkages.com

3) Verify that the size of the download matches what is stated on the website, roughly 169MB.

4) Make sure you have sufficient space on your hard drive.

5) Re-install the client.


